<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 15:13:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>丹尼洛维奇超越多勒希德夺得广州站冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/danilovic-cruises-past-dolehide-claim-guangzhou-title-2024-10-27/</link><description>周日，塞尔维亚选手奥尔加·达尼洛维奇在广州公开赛决赛中以 6-3 6-1 击败美国预选赛选手卡罗琳·多尔海德，捧起她本赛季的首座奖杯，也是她职业生涯的第二座奖杯。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 09:41:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/danilovic-cruises-past-dolehide-claim-guangzhou-title-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手郑智击败凯宁夺得东京奥运会冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/chinas-zheng-beats-kenin-claim-tokyo-title-2024-10-27/</link><description>这位 22 岁的选手今年在巴勒莫和巴黎奥运会上取得了胜利，又赢得了东京奥运会冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 06:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/chinas-zheng-beats-kenin-claim-tokyo-title-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>水手队杰克逊表示，亚冠联赛开局缓慢不应归咎于亚冠联赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-league-not-blame-slow-start-says-mariners-jackson-2024-10-27/</link><description>中央海岸水手队主教练马克·杰克逊拒绝以球队在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中的疲劳为借口，在周六连续第二场平局后，他们的澳超联赛冠军卫冕之路进展缓慢。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 05:09:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-league-not-blame-slow-start-says-mariners-jackson-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>罗伯逊在英格兰测试前赞扬全黑队的平衡阵容</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/robertson-praises-all-blacks-balanced-squad-ahead-england-test-2024-10-27/</link><description>全黑队主教练斯科特·罗伯逊相信，他的球队将为周六在特威克纳姆与英格兰队的比赛做好准备，周六，这支年轻而经验丰富的球队在横滨轻松战胜了日本队。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 03:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/robertson-praises-all-blacks-balanced-squad-ahead-england-test-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>北京猛烈抨击美国军火交易后，台湾报告中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</link><description>美国批准了一项可能为台湾提供的价值 20 亿美元的一揽子计划，其中包括向台湾提供在乌克兰经过实战考验的先进防空导弹系统。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 00:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国领导的亚投行行长批评发达国家贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</link><description>亚洲基础设施投资银行（亚投行）行长金立群周六批评发达经济体设置贸易壁垒，包括可再生能源产品，称全球经济“不再自由贸易”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:36:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，在华为处理器上发现芯片后，台积电暂停向中国公司发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</link><description>华为被限制购买该技术以保护美国国家安全。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国在美国会议上表达对关税和制裁的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国财政部周六表示，中国在华盛顿举行的两国经济工作组会议上表达了对美国关税和与俄罗斯相关制裁的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 08:16:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国导弹机构缩减关岛防御计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-missile-agency-scales-back-guam-defence-plans-2024-10-26/</link><description>美国导弹防御局周五在一份环境影响声明草案中表示，拟为关岛建造的价值数十亿美元的导弹防御系统已从原来的 22 个减少到了 16 个。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 05:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-missile-agency-scales-back-guam-defence-plans-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向台湾出售价值20亿美元的武器，其中包括乌克兰测试的导弹系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-potential-2-billion-arms-sale-taiwan-week-after-chinese-war-games-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国不断加大对台湾的军事压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 02:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-potential-2-billion-arms-sale-taiwan-week-after-chinese-war-games-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国黑客针对与哈里斯竞选活动有关的手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</link><description>一位知情人士周五表示，侵入 Verizon 系统的中国黑客瞄准了与民主党总统候选人卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 竞选活动有关联的人员使用的手机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大电动汽车部门停止讨论股权出售事宜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-ev-unit-cease-discussions-stake-sale-2024-10-25/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周五表示，其潜在卖家已决定停止出售该公司股权的谈判，该公司是负债累累的中国恒大的电动汽车部门。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 14:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-ev-unit-cease-discussions-stake-sale-2024-10-25/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈与中国续签协议几天后，北京迎来了新的天主教主教</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-gets-new-catholic-bishop-days-after-vatican-china-deal-renewal-2024-10-25/</link><description>梵蒂冈表示，在梵蒂冈和中国官员就中国任命达成协议三天后，周五任命了一位新的北京天主教助理主教。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 12:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-gets-new-catholic-bishop-days-after-vatican-china-deal-renewal-2024-10-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国寻求通过五年智能农业计划提高粮食产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-seeks-boost-food-output-with-five-year-smart-farming-plan-2024-10-25/</link><description>作为提高国内粮食产量措施的一部分，中国周五启动了一项五年行动计划，以加速整个农业产业链的数字化转型。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 11:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-seeks-boost-food-output-with-five-year-smart-farming-plan-2024-10-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心中国的高超音速武器，美国海军寻求为舰艇配备爱国者导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fearing-chinas-hypersonic-weapons-us-navy-seeks-arm-ships-with-patriot-missiles-2024-10-25/</link><description>两名高级国防官员表示，由于担心中国将部署高超音速武器击沉太平洋上的船只，美国海军正在推进一项计划，为部分船只配备爱国者拦截导弹。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 11:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fearing-chinas-hypersonic-weapons-us-navy-seeks-arm-ships-with-patriot-missiles-2024-10-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>